## Session Templates

### Standard Session Structure
```
SessionName/
├── README.md           # Session overview
├── metadata.json       # Session data
├── artifacts/          # Generated outputs
├── learnings.md        # Insights gained
└── performance.md      # Metrics and analysis
```

### Session Metadata Format
```json
{
  "session_id": "uuid",
  "agent": "{{agent_name}}",
  "start_time": "timestamp",
  "end_time": "timestamp",
  "session_type": "type",
  "objectives": ["list"],
  "outcomes": ["list"],
  "collaborators": ["list"],
  "metrics": {},
  "learnings": ["list"]
}
```

